{"tid":1420300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係深水埗街坊，琴晚無示警下中彈","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:35:51.000Z","uid":268221,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"94cefb4a9d3d48edca437358f8bfe6aca16f7e4b","tid":1420300,"uid":268221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"我係深水埗街坊，琴晚同過百街坊喺示威者同警方中間的欽州街／長沙灣道交界吊警，勸佢哋收隊。我哋一群只係企喺旁邊，無夾喺兩邊中間。結果，警察喺只舉咗黑旗情況下，向我哋街坊方向射擊海綿彈。我肚中槍，好彩無大礙，只係紅咗同有抽住痛感覺。<br />\n呢班爛仔離L晒譜，想驅散街坊開催淚彈就可以，無需要向呢個方向射擊海綿彈。當街坊係發泄工具。"},{"pid":"8e178d1fc6f33470c1a1c2a307d34242707dc4de","tid":1420300,"uid":102732,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:15:15.000Z","msg":"上民間記者會講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6d7be97c4a9f0f99ddb884ec98156ff6539b10","tid":1420300,"uid":125619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:15:39.000Z","msg":"有無傷勢圖? 有可以宣傳下佢地濫暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c0202dde42fcb55f173134c84acace25e1747a","tid":1420300,"uid":268221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec6d7be97c4a9f0f99ddb884ec98156ff6539b10","tid":1420300,"uid":125619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:15:39.000Z","msg":"有無傷勢圖? 有可以宣傳下佢地濫暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:19:20.000Z","msg":"仲紅緊，但好輕微。嗰時地下有彈殼，但無影到，查返應該係海綿彈。"},{"pid":"6675db447e3224baf555392e1a04ba17b405ae44","tid":1420300,"uid":207641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:19:39.000Z","msg":"禁錯負皮 sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea13ce89199cf18f33355cbf37b3b36c91d9796e","tid":1420300,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:22:03.000Z","msg":"幫連仔講返句公道說話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420183\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/142018